==== SOURCE

https://emerj.com/ai-sector-overviews/airlines-use-artificial-intelligence/

==== AGENT

Kumba Sennaar, journalist covering tech research breakthroughs.

==== GOAL

See how americas 4 largest airlines use machine learning.

==== DATA

Various data obtained from passengers. From passport photos to size luggage arriving at each gate.

==== METHODS

Smart logistics, Machine learning algorithms to help automate airline operations. AI assistants and facial recognition.

==== RESULTS

Delta airlines have already introduced self  service kiosks incorporating facial recognition. Southwest airlines are using machine learning techniques which is enhancing data mining

==== COMMENTS